videos.description: Wake Forest's Doral Moore catches an alley oop from Brandon Childress and throws it down with two hands.
videos.headline: Moore goes flying for the catch and slam

videos.description: Wake Forest's Bryant Crawford throws a great pass inside that sets up John Collins for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Good passing sets up a big Wake Forest dunk

videos.description: Wake Forest's Bryant Crawford knocks down a 3-pointer before the end of the first half to give the Deamon Deacons a 5 point lead.
videos.headline: Crawford nails a three to beat the buzzer

videos.description: Notre Dame's Temple Gibb drives the baseline, then finishes between a couple defenders and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Gibbs drives and finishes a tough lay-in

videos.description: Konstantinos Mitoglou hits a shot fading away and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Mitoglou finishes acrobatic score and draws a foul

videos.description: V..J. Beachem creates space for himself, then connects on  a 3-pointer late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Beachem hits a big 3-pointer

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell drains a 3-pointer to extend Notre Dame's lead late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Farrell drains pull up 3-pointer
